\centering
\includegraphics[width=0.8\textwidth]{figs/ParameterFit.pdf}
\caption{Fit between SOEP data and theory (q = 0.641) for number of at-
tachments. Data from Markov chain, confidence intervals from 1000 runs
of agent-based simulation with 965 agents. Insets: Model behavior for first 10 and first 20 steps
of the panel. (This plot matches Figure 2 (Left) in \textcite{Metz.Lorenz2013Becomewhoyou}.)} \label{fig:MetzLorenz3}
